      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "This notebook demonstrates a simple **DPO (Direct Preference Optimization) workflow for LLM alignment using a small custom preference dataset and Hugging Face TRL.**\n",
        "\n",
        "What this demo shows\n",
        "how to format pairwise preference data as prompt / chosen / rejected\n",
        "how to **fine-tune a small instruct model with DPO**\n",
        "how to compare model outputs before and after preference alignment\n",
        "Main references\n",
        "Rafailov et al. (2023), Direct Preference Optimization: The Language Model is Secretly a Reward Model\n",
        "Hugging Face TRL documentation for DPOTrainer"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "NAM-VgVocj2_"
      },
      "id": "NAM-VgVocj2_"
    },
